<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>206</hymn_number>
<title>JESUH THI LAWNG IN CH206</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka sualnak zei in thiang lai, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko. Zeidah a
 ka damter lai? Jesuh thi lawngin ka dam lai.

[C1]
   Maw thletmi sung bik thi, Hawhra bang rantertu, Cerhti dang ka tong
   lo, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko.

[V2]
 Keimah thianter awk ca-ah, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko. Keimah sual
 ngaihthiam awkah, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko.

[C2]
   Maw thletmi sung bik thi, Hawhra bang rantertu, Cerhti dang ka tong
   lo, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko.

[V3]
 Keimah sual ca ingtu ah, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko. Atu tiang zei
 kaa hlei lo, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko.

[C3]
   Maw thletmi sung bik thi, Hawhra bang rantertu, Cerhti dang ka tong
   lo, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko.

[V4]
 Ka ruahchan lungnemnak ca, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko; Keimah
 miding sinak ah, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko.

[C4]
   Maw thletmi sung bik thi, Hawhra bang rantertu, Cerhti dang ka tong
   lo, Jesuh thi lawngin a thiang ko.</lyrics>
</song>